race.comment: FEDERAL DUKE (6) put in a much better performance last start when in the placings at Gosford behind Intense Power (22.53) in a Grade 5. Has the early speed to give a sight. Has a strong record from box 6, including three wins. One of the leading chances. STORYLINE (5) is mixing form lately, finishing out of the placings last time at Gosford but was a Maiden winner two back at Gosford. Has the ability and looks a key chance here. DELICATE ROSE (1) finds it hard to break through. Finished second (20.48) at Gunnedah latest and might be close to finding winning form again. Leading chance. DRINK ROSE (2) can sneak into the finish with the right run.
